title: Snow Day With Her Professor - Amy Aday.epub
description: Selena finds herself stranded on the side of the road during an impending blizzard. She is grateful when her rather hot literature professor happens along and offers to help. They end up at his place waiting for the storm to pass. But soon, the college freshman finds it hard to resist her sexy, older and more experienced professor. Will he give in to her? And if he does, will she be able to handle what he has in mind?
